[IMG]http://i98.photobucket.com/albums/l273/bikerbabe458/skyrim/pskull.jpg[/IMG]

Far below Dragon Bridge is a lost sanctuary of the Dragon Priests. Here is where they kept the six magical crystal dragon skulls. In a forgotten cave, now infested with Falmer, under the bridge is where you must go to retrieve these crystal skulls. Each skull has a different power but all can be equipped at the same time. Be wary adventurer.




DO NOT upload any other sites or use without my permission. Thanks BG
